/*
  Description:
    List of applications to be installed via InstallApps.ps1.

  Categories:
    MainApps:       Apps which you usually want to install on every system.
    AdditionalApps: Apps which you might want to install on some systems (choose which).
    Tools:          Developer tools and utilities or apps without GUI.
    Deprecated:     Apps which are no longer needed or used.

  source:
    winget:   Install via winget using the provided id.
    internet: Download from the provided url.
    local:    Install from a local path under "installers/" (include the installer file in the path).
    terminal: Install via a terminal or powershell command.

  Usage:
    Run GenerateConfigs.ps1, or copy this file to config/apps.json and remove all comments.
*/

